  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "AI-powered decision support systems provide farmers with real-time insights by integrating data from sensors, weather forecasts, and markets (Tupalo, 2024).",
    "These systems optimize irrigation, fertilization, and pest control, reducing environmental impact while increasing efficiency (Ali et al., 2025).",
    "AI also aids in identifying crop diseases and nutrient deficiencies through image recognition and sensor analysis (Usigbe et al., 2024).",
    "ML models further refine drought response predictions by evaluating interactions between continuous and categorical variables (Liang et al., 2024).",
    "Beyond cultivation, AI improves post-harvest logistics and supply chain management, optimizing solar dryers, cold storage, and equipment maintenance (Usigbe et al., 2024; Kumar D. et al., 2024)."
  ],
